snippet.title: Caterwaul - early stage gameplay
snippet.description:
https://moult.itch.io/caterwaul

Caterwaul is a hybrid story/rhythm/puzzle game, inspired by Rock Star Ate My Hamster and other quirky British games of yore. Tour beautiful Clowdenshire, meet weird cats, play gigs, and work the biz!
